    <http://w3id.org/def/guia#hasCompetency> <http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/cb-CB10>,<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/cg-CG5>,<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/cg-CG6>,<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/t-T2>,<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/t-T3>,<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/t-T6> .

<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/course-guide-ANXPRCL001> guide:hasDidacticResource <http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/resource-Bibliography>;
    sch:description "This module supports students whose first language is not English over a semester of academic study, and helps them to refine their writing through extensive language input, practice and feedback. The syllabus focuses on issues such as coping with organisation and coherence in the text and with range and accuracy of the language used."@en ;
    guide:inLanguage "Castellano"@en .

